Installing trivy:
-> wget -O trivy.tar.gz https://github.com/aquasecurity/trivy/releases/download/v0.54.1/trivy_0.54.1_Linux-64bit.tar.gz
After installing it shows below file;
-> trivy.tar.gz 
Now extract the above file:
tar -zxvf trivy.tar.gz trivy
Then move tge ifle:
sudo mv trivy /usr/local/bin/
then check version:
trivy --version
Version: 0.54.1
